description: Urijah and Zane have been friends since they graduated from high school. So, only about a year, and Urijah had no clue that Zane was bi. He didn't know until he lost a bet with Zane. They bet over a football game and Urijah had no idea what he would have to do if he lost but he certainly did not expect anything sexual. Well, he was wrong, way wrong. Zane said since he lost the bet he had to blow him. Not to be a sore loser, Urijah went along with it. After all, it is just a bj, Zane, however, decided he was gonna fuck him as well, watch and see what happens. You will be pleasantly surprised.
title: Big Zane
